lead_paragraph: There will be no let-up for Barcelona after they were unravelled by the intense pressing of Manchester City, with the La Liga champions set for a gruelling encounter with a new look Sevilla side marshalled by attacking zealot Jorge Sampaoli on Sunday.

headline.print_headline: Dishevelled Barca Set for Another Testing Game With Sevilla
headline.main: Dishevelled Barca Set for Another Testing Game With Sevilla
